@desc Arrange files by name, size, type, or when they were changed.

[comment]
  May benefit from figures illustrating the different views.

You can sort files in different ways in a folder, for example by sorting them
in order of date or file size. See $link[>#ways] below for a list of
common ways to sort files. See $link[>nautilus-views] for information on
how to change the default sort order.

The way that you can sort files depends on the $em(folder view) that you
are using. You can change the current view using the list or icon buttons in the
toolbar.


== Icon view
   [#icon-view]

To sort files in a different order, click the view options button in the
